{% comment %}
  JavaScript for A/B Testing

  Option 1: Manual Weekly Rotation
  - Uncomment the variant you want to test this week
  - Track conversions in Google Analytics by variant ID

  Option 2: Random Split (for Google Optimize alternative)
  - Randomly shows one of three variants
  - Add event tracking to measure which performs best
{% endcomment %}

<script>
// Option 1: Manual - Set which variant to show
// const activeVariant = 'a'; // Change to 'b' or 'c' for other variants

// Option 2: Automatic Random Split (50/50/50 across three variants)
const variants = ['a', 'b', 'c'];
const activeVariant = variants[Math.floor(Math.random() * variants.length)];

// Show the active variant
document.querySelectorAll('.hero-variant').forEach(el => {
  el.style.display = 'none';
});
document.getElementById('hero-variant-' + activeVariant).style.display = 'block';

// Track which variant was shown
if (typeof gtag !== 'undefined') {
  gtag('event', 'hero_variant_shown', {
    'event_category': 'AB_Test',
    'event_label': 'hero_variant_' + activeVariant,
    'value': activeVariant
  });
}

// Track CTA clicks by variant
document.querySelectorAll('.hero-variant .btn-primary').forEach(btn => {
  btn.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
    const variant = this.closest('.hero-variant').dataset.variant;
    if (typeof gtag !== 'undefined') {
      gtag('event', 'hero_cta_click', {
        'event_category': 'AB_Test',
        'event_label': 'hero_variant_' + variant,
        'value': variant
      });
    }
  });
});
</script>

{% comment %}
  Google Analytics 4 Setup:

  1. Events will be tracked as:
     - hero_variant_shown (which variant was displayed)
     - hero_cta_click (which variant's CTA was clicked)

  2. In GA4, create a funnel:
     - Step 1: hero_variant_shown
     - Step 2: hero_cta_click
     - Step 3: add_to_cart
     - Step 4: purchase

  3. Compare conversion rates:
     - Variant A: Control conversion rate
     - Variant B: Emotional conversion rate
     - Variant C: Social proof conversion rate

  4. Winning criteria:
     - Run test for 2-3 weeks
     - Minimum 1,000 visitors per variant
     - Winner needs 95% statistical significance
     - Use https://abtestguide.com/calc/ to verify
{% endcomment %}
